  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study was to identify the etiology of events and demographics of patients
      that experience complications requiring activation of the Rapid Response Team (RRT) during
      the first 24 h following anesthetic care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
