  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Identifying post-operative criteria for activation of Rapid Response Teams (RRTs) in caring for the pediatric population using Pediatric Early Warning Scores (PEWS)</measure>
    <time_frame>24 hours post-operatively</time_frame>
    <description>To retrospectively identify the etiologies associated with a need to engage Rapid Response Teams (RRTs) to promote frequent assessments and early interventions among clinically deteriorating hospitalized pediatric patients.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
